{"tid":1610653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"最後再講一次 偽勇武 和理非 做人做豬自己揀","createTime":"2019-10-01T18:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:20:53.000Z","uid":90615,"like":36,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e134d4ea0ca539786fdd2522f892857e14805437","tid":1610653,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:47:45.000Z","msg":"你地可以繼續每次出黎都一有tg就保特上身<br />\n200米外見到狗就驚撚到亂嗌人退<br />\n咁下場好簡單<br />\n前線手足每次死幾十個<br />\n死晒無人出黎<br />\n你地亦都有第二條路<br />\n每次出黎收下把口 用下隻眼<br />\n望下視線所及有無狗 <br />\n無既 就算聽到退都唔好跑<br />\n眼望前方一二一二<br />\n前線手足一叫停 即刻一二一二上返前<br />\n用人數令啲狗唔敢亂黎<br />\n<br />\n係呀 見狗就跑好撚安全 <br />\n今日cosplay完聽日又可以做返豬 <br />\n仲可以開IG打下卡share下文宣買贖罪劵<br />\n但你有無諗過你害死幾多手足?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家又唔撚係叫你去比狗打<br />\n你唔退 前線手足唔退 你咪又撚係後排</span><br />\n會有人代你去打架啦<br />\n唔好panic呢件事有無咁難呀? <br />\n咁難不如除低你個雙罐豬嘴比人然後返屋企睇直播啦"},{"pid":"ea6d66e21c0ed0d5245f87015ffe62d4aa52a27d","tid":1610653,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b7532c97103d763a7b4ba3f5e1736df49496d8","tid":1610653,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:02:02.000Z","msg":"想輸咪一齊輸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ceda417cf24209d4962156b2b754aeaefef013c","tid":1610653,"uid":206370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:22:29.000Z","msg":"agger 唔好比假希望真勇武"},{"pid":"27e8e3daf5896a2fb8f748e1fed466ead04eb388","tid":1610653,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:28:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b99df53a16488e8beb5a3eddf85482a1a2d61e65","tid":1610653,"uid":208262